## 1. Decision

`tools/thiên` is promoted from simple launcher to operator console.

## 2. Operator Commands

- `tools/thiên help`
- `tools/thiên routes`
- `tools/thiên status`
- `tools/thiên health`
- `tools/thiên restart`
- `tools/thiên stop`
- `tools/thiên log`
- `tools/thiên gate`
- `tools/thiên doctor`
- `tools/thiên resolve <name>`
- `tools/thiên emit <type> [json_payload]`
- `tools/thiên open [apps|audit|tam|screens|nauion|core|all]`
- `tools/thiên run <file.sira> [...args]`

## 3. Runtime Layers

- `anc://` = identity protocol
- `.sira` = namespace / artifact layer
- `tools/thiên` = operator console
- `http://` = browser transport adapter
- SmartLink = resolver / coupling layer
